                "2. Fundamentals -- 2.1 Visualization -- 2.2 Human-computer interaction -- 2.3 Interaction in visualization -- 2.4 The visualization-interaction gap -- 2.5 Interaction, useful or harmful? -- 2.6 Implementing interactive visualization -- 2.7 Summarizing thoughts --",
